Kerry Rossall https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Kerry_Rossall 0 Kerry Darrell Rossall (born June 23, 1947) is an American stuntman, actor and producer. He is best known for portraying "Mike from San Diego" in the 1979 war film Apocalypse Now. Kerry_Darrell_Rossall ( born June_23_,_1947 ) is an_American_stuntman , actor_and_producer .
